snippet: Missy Franklin claimed a record sixth gold medal at the world swimming championships in Barcelona, Spain, swimming the leadoff leg for the Americans in the 4x100-meter medley relay.
abstract: American swimmer Missy Franklin claims a record sixth gold medal at world championships in Barcelona, Spain.
